OL,5,BThe Chunky Fringe service.   W +//'    
OL,7,BUnlike the previousEBlock PartyBevents,
OL,8,Bwhere only attendees were able to edit 
OL,9,Bpages,E"Chunkytext"Bis open to all via 
OL,10,Bthe internet. Time will tell if that is
OL,11,Ba wise idea!                           
OL,13,BSee theEuser guideBon page 103 for more
OL,14,Bdetails.                               
OL,16,BChunkytext contains a mixture of newly 
OL,17,Bcreated articles and artwork, alongside
OL,18,ETeletext LtdBpages recovered from VHS. 
