OL,7,B                                       
OL,8,BHello, children. Here are my top tips  
OL,9,Bfor a safe and fun event in Harrow.    
OL,10,E                                       
OL,11,U /EIt can be tough meeting new people, 
OL,12,E   but the Digitiser crowd are lovely. 
OL,13,E                                       
OL,14,U /EIf travelling alone, make sure that 
OL,15,E   somebody knows what your plans are. 
OL,16,E                                       
OL,17,U /EDrink sensibly, and don't even THINK
OL,18,E   about stealing MY BINS as a TROPHY. 
